      "description": "Non-planar double box with one massive propagator for light $N_f$ two-loop corrections to $gg \\to t\\bar{t}$. Three master integrals with propagator powers $\\{1,1,1,1,0,0,1,1,1\\}$ and irreducible numerator insertions $k_1 \\cdot k_2$ and $(k_1 \\cdot k_2)^2$. Most involved topology in the paper. Thresholds in all three channels $s, t, u$. Results in GPLs with argument $y$ and weights $\\{-1, 0, -x, -1/x, -(1+x^2)/x, -(1-x+x^2)/x\\}$ or argument $x$ and weights $\\{-1, 0, 1, [1+o^2], [1-o+o^2]\\}$. Coproduct-augmented symbol analysis yields simplifications for poles in $\\varepsilon$. Mellin-Barnes representation given in Appendix A.",
